OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan has backed calls for
OL,7,Fthe possession of small quantities of
OL,8,Fnatural cannabis to be decriminalised,
OL,9,Fsaying current rules "cannot be
OL,10,Fjustified".
OL,12,FThe Mayor of London said a report by
OL,13,Fthe independent London Drugs
OL,14,FCommission (LDC) published on
OL,15,FWednesday had provided "a compelling,
OL,16,Fevidence-based case" for
OL,17,Fdecriminalisation and urged the
OL,18,FGovernment to consider the move.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@JO]wD@XOUxD@TO]
