OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,FHowever Sir Mark Rowley, the head of
OL,7,Fthe UK's largest police force, has
OL,8,Fopposed the Mayor of London's call to
OL,9,Fdecriminalise some cannabis possession.
OL,11,FThe Metropolitan Police Commissioner
OL,12,Fsaid drug use is a "big issue" for
OL,13,Fcommunities, driving anti-social
OL,14,Fbehaviour and acquisitive crime, and
OL,15,Fthat a change in the law on cannabis
OL,16,Fis "not something we're calling for".
OL,26,@tD@TOUtD@^O]xD@DOUxD@dO]
