OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,FSet up by Sir Sadiq in 2022 and
OL,7,Fchaired by former lord chancellor Lord
OL,8,FCharlie Falconer, the LDC found the
OL,9,Fcurrent laws on cannabis were
OL,10,F"disproportionate to the harms it can
OL,11,Fpose" following a study of how the
OL,12,Fdrug is policed around the world.
OL,14,FIt also found cannabis policing
OL,15,F"continues to focus on particular
OL,16,Fethnic communities", damaging
OL,17,Frelations between the police and those
OL,18,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@EO]wD@AOUxD@SO]
