OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1748605861
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"Those who suffer from the adverse
OL,7,Feffects of cannabis ` which may be a
OL,8,Fsmall percentage of users but it is a
OL,9,Fhigh number of people ` need reliable,
OL,10,Fconsistent medical and other support.
OL,11,FAnd there needs to be much more
OL,12,Feducation on the risks of cannabis
OL,13,Fuse."
OL,15,FUnder current laws, cannabis is a
OL,16,Fclass B drug and those found in
OL,17,Fpossession face a fine or imprisonment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@EO]
