OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley said decriminalising some
OL,8,Fcannabis possession "is not something
OL,9,Fwe're calling for", following the
OL,10,Fmayor's calls.
OL,12,FWhile he acknowledged that changing
OL,13,Fthe law is a matter for Parliament, he
OL,14,Ftold the BBC: "At the moment we see
OL,15,Fdrugs being at the centre of a lot of
OL,16,Fcrime, whether it's drug dealing ...
OL,17,Fis so linked to violence, the county
OL,18,Flines we close down ` over 80% of the
OL,19,Fpeople behind those lines have got
OL,20,Fviolent backgrounds.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@RO]vD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/16
