PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1748605861
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"We see a lot of communities
OL,7,Fcomplaining about public drug use, and
OL,8,Fthat's a big issue in terms of anti-
OL,9,Fsocial behaviour."
OL,11,FHe added: "We're chasing around people
OL,12,Fwho are using drugs in public, which
OL,13,Fis concern to communities. We see drug
OL,14,Fusers becoming addicted and that
OL,15,Fdriving acquisitive crime. It's a big
OL,16,Fpart in our current operations. If the
OL,17,Flaw changes we'll change around that,
OL,18,Fbut it's not something we're calling
OL,19,Ffor."
OL,26,@qD@RO]sD@KOU{D@EO]
