OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1748605861
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"We have no intention of reclassifying
OL,7,Fcannabis from a class B substance
OL,8,Funder the Misuse of Drugs Act, and our
OL,9,Ffocus is continuing to work with
OL,10,Fpartners across health, policing and
OL,11,Fwider public services to drive down
OL,12,Fdrug use, ensure more people receive
OL,13,Ftimely treatment and support, and make
OL,14,Four communities and streets safer."
OL,16,FLDC deputy chairwoman Janet Hills, a
OL,17,Fformer Metropolitan Police detective,
OL,18,Fsaid the report was "a driver for
OL,19,Fchange in our community" and called
OL,20,Ffor "a more balanced and compassionate
OL,21,Fapproach to policing in our city".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@cO]zD@UOU{D@XO]|D@EOU}D@aO]
