OL,6,FResponding to the report, Sir Sadiq
OL,7,Fsaid: "I've long been clear that we
OL,8,Fneed fresh thinking on how to reduce
OL,9,Fthe substantial harms associated with
OL,10,Fdrug-related crime in our communities.
OL,12,F"The London Drugs Commission report
OL,13,Fmakes a compelling, evidenced-based
OL,14,Fcase for the decriminalisation of
OL,15,Fpossession of small quantities of
OL,16,Fnatural cannabis which the Government
OL,17,Fshould consider.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/16
