OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1748605861
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"It says that the current sentencing
OL,7,Ffor those caught in possession of
OL,8,Fnatural cannabis cannot be justified
OL,9,Fgiven its relative harm and people's
OL,10,Fexperience of the justice system.
OL,12,F"We must recognise that better
OL,13,Feducation, improved healthcare and
OL,14,Fmore effective, equitable policing of
OL,15,Fcannabis use are long overdue."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/16
