OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fwill continue to work with partners
OL,8,Facross health, policing and wider
OL,9,Fpublic services to drive down drug
OL,10,Fuse, ensure more people receive timely
OL,11,Ftreatment and support, and make our
OL,12,Fstreets and communities safer.
OL,14,F"The government has no intention of
OL,15,Freclassifying cannabis from a Class B
OL,16,Fsubstance under the Misuse of Drugs
OL,17,FAct."
OL,26,@nD@bOUvD@AOUyD@EO]
