OL,11,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp
OL,12,Fsaid: "Possession of cannabis should
OL,13,Fnot be decriminalised like this. We
OL,14,Fhave seen some US and Canadian cities
OL,15,Fdevastated by soft policies on
OL,16,Faddictive and harmful drugs ` now
OL,17,FSadiq Khan wants to send London the
OL,18,Fsame way.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
