OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"Cannabis is illegal for a reason.
OL,7,FCannabis is associated with anti-
OL,8,Fsocial behaviour and heavy use can
OL,9,Flead to serious psychosis and severed
OL,10,Fmental health problems.
OL,12,F"US and Canadian cities which tried
OL,13,Fthis approach have ended up as crime-
OL,14,Fridden ghettos with stupefied addicts
OL,15,Fon the streets and law-abiding
OL,16,Fcitizens frightened to go there.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/16
