OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Current cannabis rules
OL,4,C'cannot be justified'
OL,6,F"Sadiq Khan is more interested in
OL,7,Fpolitically correct posturing for the
OL,8,Fbenefit of his left-wing friends than
OL,9,Fhe is making London a safe and nice
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,F"I completely oppose these plans. But
OL,13,Fwith a weak Labour Government in
OL,14,Fpower, there's no telling how they
OL,15,Fwill react. We must stop soft Sadiq."
